<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c5">سُنَّتُ من:</span> سُنَّتُ الْأَوَّلِينَ <span class="c4">[الأنفال: ٣٨]</span>.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
